'''Sotheby's''' is an international auction house, that over the years has sold many rare and unique Tolkien items (which also are described and reprinted in their [[:Category:Sotheby's catalogues|auction catalogues]]), perhaps most notably [[Letters not published in The Letters of J.R.R. Tolkien|letters not published in ''The Letters of J.R.R. Tolkien'']].
